  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A 3d game similar to the classic Spy vs Spy series. You are inside a 3D virtual maze and have to compete against another human player or the computer to find the treasures, objects and keys before your oponent does. To do this you can use your weapon or phisical attacks against the oponent to stealth his treasures.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Kick! Punch! Pissed off! The inhumane and evil maze battle is here!\nSetting traps, flying tools, direct attacks, you can place radical obstacles as many as you like!\nSeize the key before your opponent and locate the exit!\nIn this maze battle game, the person who runs around and escapes first from the 3D maze wins.\nEquipped with an automatic maze-generating function, you will not get bored with this game!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
